es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如搵人整set窈窕淑女icon抗衡下算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好牙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過連帝話下set要審批<br />\n想長駐?發下夢先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥婆：上咗架就係神仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他：要審批，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/151923_eb5353f7282b921a555855d21745773b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F151923_eb5353f7282b921a555855d21745773b.jpg&h=a4735af1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b4c87a35d9b61c2f09824dc32655a6ca6da529c","tid":46942,"uid":47500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"想上位,收皮啦.jpg"},{"pid":"d1f9145a8695bd5475cffd7af944afbb2f3ae275","tid":46942,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:05:22.000Z","msg":"係呀2000負皮都嚟緊一齊葡萄你<br />\n呀唔係係個原創user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3db86e2d102af4ff9ae24588d4240910b93afc","tid":46942,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"過千人葡萄一個肥婆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b4c61fe9f12f4d7d03e3a4782d016a524a8e9a","tid":46942,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/161800_d2c606b0a118802efc73bd9573385bd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F161800_d2c606b0a118802efc73bd9573385bd1.jpg&h=3d2e77f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20bfd72a3ce7c9756395fc19c67d9d0da109279a","tid":46942,"uid":1035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老老竇竇<br />\n如果套icon唔係肥婆樣我諗應該無乜人會反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊有可能個反感大成咁, 班人一係比肥婆強姦過, 一係以為自己上連登好撚型, 少少柒野都唔得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都識講係柒嘢<br />\n人點可能咁輕易去接受柒嘢？<br />\n仲要係一個流量大、會員多嘅論壇<br />\n你一句唔該就要成個論壇嘅人睇呢套嘢喺個壇裡面飛嚟飛去<br />\n都講唔通啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家個情況就好似<br />\n1000人入面有100個人成日都食榴連<br />\n然後房主見榴連咁多人食<br />\n就話：不如大家一齊食榴連囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果無出過聲嗰900個人<br />\n無論鐘意唔鐘意 都被迫聞住嗰100人食榴連嘅味一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a325b4bd3f6cfdcd8a974efa45fc901c6baf06c","tid":46942,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}